descriptionNullable:
### Context

When dealing with large datasets for model training, GPU is too slow. So this data is created to leverage TPU for model training


### Content

The dataset consist o of  face landmarks  extracted using mediapipe for Facial Emotion Recognition tasks


### Acknowledgements

The data was collected and extracted by https://github.com/GiangVu0912 a student at Coderschool.


### Inspiration

For having a better FER model for future usages
